.TH "LIGHTNING-INVOICE-WAIT" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-invoice-wait \- wait for an invoice to be paid
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning invoice-wait
.I label
.RB [ --timeout
.IR N ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Blocks until the named invoice is paid or the timeout (default: 60 s)
expires, using CLN's
.B waitinvoice
RPC.
.PP
Output when paid:
.nf
{"label":"...","status":"paid","paid_at":N,"payment_hash":"..."}
.fi
Output when timed out:
.nf
{"label":"...","status":"timeout"}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-invoice-create (1),
.BR lightning-invoice-status (1)
